  "source": "Carl Sagan",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T06:13:38Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 101,
  "quote": "Look up at the stars and not down at your feet.",
  "source": "Stephen Hawking",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T09:10:26Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 102,
  "quote": "For small creatures such as we the vastness is bearable only through love.",
  "source": "Carl Sagan",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T11:36:42Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 103,
  "quote": "天下万物生于有，有生于无。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第四十章",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T13:41:35Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 104,
  "quote": "大方无隅，大器晚成，大音希声，大象无形。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第四十一章",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T15:29:30Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 105,
  "quote": "上善若水。水善利万物而不争。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第八章",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T17:11:18Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 106,
  "quote": "知者不言，言者不知。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第五十六章",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T19:03:40Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 107,
  "quote": "人法地，地法天，天法道，道法自然。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第二十五章",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T20:53:04Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 108,
  "quote": "天地有大美而不言。",
  "source": "庄子 · 知北游",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T22:00:22Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 109,
  "quote": "至人之用心若镜，不将不迎，应而不藏。",
  "source": "庄子 · 应帝王",
  "updated": "2026-07-16T23:55:20Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 110,
  "quote": "独与天地精神往来。",
  "source": "庄子 · 天下",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T02:23:25Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 111,
  "quote": "Stay hungry, stay foolish.",
  "source": "Steve Jobs",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T05:38:28Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 112,
  "quote": "大音希声，大象无形。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第四十一章",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T08:02:54Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 113,
  "quote": "道生一，一生二，二生三，三生万物。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第四十二章",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T10:43:17Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 114,
  "quote": "致虚极，守静笃。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第十六章",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T12:06:04Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 115,
  "quote": "天地之间，其犹橐龠乎？虚而不屈，动而愈出。",
  "source": "老子 · 道德经 第五章",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T14:39:55Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 116,
  "quote": "空故纳万境，静故了群动。",
  "source": "苏轼 · 送参寥师",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T16:11:46Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 117,
  "quote": "色不异空，空不异色；色即是空，空即是色。",
  "source": "般若波罗蜜多心经",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T18:02:05Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 118,
  "quote": "菩提本无树，明镜亦非台。本来无一物，何处惹尘埃。",
  "source": "慧能 · 六祖坛经",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T20:02:34Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 119,
  "quote": "一切有为法，如梦幻泡影，如露亦如电，应作如是观。",
  "source": "金刚经",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T21:49:01Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 120,
  "quote": "宇宙便是吾心，吾心即是宇宙。",
  "source": "陆九渊",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T22:44:17Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 121,
  "quote": "江畔何人初见月？江月何年初照人？",
  "source": "张若虚 · 春江花月夜",
  "updated": "2026-07-17T23:48:42Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 122,
  "quote": "行到水穷处，坐看云起时。",
  "source": "王维 · 终南别业",
  "updated": "2026-07-18T02:04:26Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 123,
  "quote": "千江有水千江月，万里无云万里天。",
  "source": "嘉泰普灯录",
  "updated": "2026-07-18T05:21:01Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 124,
  "quote": "Empty your mind, be formless, shapeless — like water.",
  "source": "Bruce Lee",
  "updated": "2026-07-18T07:43:04Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 125,
  "quote": "The true sign of intelligence is not knowledge but imagination.",
  "source": "Albert Einstein",
  "updated": "2026-07-18T09:20:05Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 126,
  "quote": "The quieter you become, the more you can hear.",
  "source": "Rumi",
  "updated": "2026-07-18T10:59:06Z"
}
,
{
  "index": 127,
  "quote": "In the midst of movement and chaos, keep stillness inside of you.",
